# Serve a real image for legacy /favicon.ico probes; the SPA catch-all otherwise
# returns index.html (HTML) for /favicon.ico. Modern clients use the <link rel=icon> PNGs.
/favicon.ico  /favicon-light-mode.png  200

# Note: /package.json (a leaked Vite build artifact) is NOT handled here. A
# _redirects 404 rewrite to a non-existent target is not a supported Cloudflare
# Pages mechanism; the file is instead deleted from the explorer build output in
# the deploy workflow (drop leaked artifacts (explorer)), so there is no asset
# to serve.
